query: SELECT p.id, p.name, p.civilId, COUNT(*) as test_count FROM patients p JOIN virologyTests vt ON p.id = vt.patientId WHERE vt.viralLoad IS NOT NULL AND vt.viralLoad != '' GROUP BY p.id HAVING test_count >= 4 ORDER BY test_count DESC LIMIT 5;
